The main Pull-down menu gave you choice of Soup & salad, Main course and
dessert.  If you 'pull-down' the dessert sub-menu, you get this selection.

This is a sub-menu 'pulled down' from a main menu.  It operates like other
menus.  Select an item with either the UP and DOWN arrow or by striking
the keys corresponding to the KEYS above (1, 2, 3, ... ).  When you have
the desired item, select it with the ENTER key.

Use the F2 key for an explanation of your choices in this sub-menu.
Hit the ESCape key or Alt-X to leave this menu and return to the main
Pull-down menu.  Use the F4 key to change text colors.
